{"data": [{"id": "4747014", "title": "First Internet Bancorp: Floating Debt Securities Offer High Single-Digit Yield", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"woman sit in front restaurant and shop online with credit card\" data-id=\"2185938635\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Miljan \u017divkovi\u0107/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction</strong></h2> <p>Although I\u2019m currently not a shareholder of First Internet Bancorp (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INBK\" title=\"First Internet Bancorp\">INBK</a></span>) I'm keeping an eye on its financial results as I still <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4701988-first-internet-bancorp-bottoming-net-interest-margin-bodes-well-future\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4701988-first-internet-bancorp-bottoming-net-interest-margin-bodes-well-future\" target=\"_blank\">have a long position in its baby bonds</a> which recently started to offer the bondholders</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747014-first-internet-bancorp-floating-debt-securities-offer-high-single-digit-yield", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 18:30:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747481", "title": "Tesla: Major Q4 Delivery Disappointment", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Israeli Prime Minister Netanyahu Meets With Elon Musk At Tesla In Fremont, CA\" data-id=\"1689016078\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"914px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Justin Sullivan/Getty Images News</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Over the last couple of months, one of the biggest winners in the market has been <b>Tesla, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSLA\" title=\"Tesla, Inc.\">TSLA</a></span>). The electric vehicle (\u201cEV\u201d) maker has seen its shares soar after former President Donald Trump was</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747481-tesla-major-q4-delivery-disappointment", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 18:24:01", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747494", "title": "January 2025 Perspective", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Conceptual image of man using smartphone to view bar graph\" data-id=\"1359134494\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1138px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">We Are</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><span>What\u2019s New</span></h2> <p>The holidays were far less happy for financial markets than the first 11 months of the year had been.</p> <p>We came into the month with yields on the rise, and this continued into the inflation print</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747494-january-2025-perspective", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 18:10:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747490", "title": "Total Return Forecasts: Major Asset Classes - January 3, 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Abstract trading chart with big data and infographics. 3D Fintech concept background with glowing candle chart\" data-id=\"1752905583\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">da-kuk</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The expected return over the long run for the Global Market Index (GMI) held steady in December vs. the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741817-total-return-forecasts-major-asset-classes-december-3-2024\" rel=\"noopener\">previous month</a>. The unchanged forecast, based on three models defined below, reflects a second month with the highest return outlook in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747490-total-return-forecasts-major-asset-classes-january-3-2025", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 18:02:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747482", "title": "Palo Alto Networks: Don't Ignore The Warning Signs (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426100645/image_1426100645.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Palo Alto Networks\" data-id=\"1426100645\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426100645/image_1426100645.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426100645/image_1426100645.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426100645/image_1426100645.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426100645/image_1426100645.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426100645/image_1426100645.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426100645/image_1426100645.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426100645/image_1426100645.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426100645/image_1426100645.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">hapabapa</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>When I think of cybersecurity providers to invest in, Palo Alto Networks (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PANW\" title=\"Palo Alto Networks, Inc.\">PANW</a></span>) often comes to the top of my watchlist. And cybersecurity is a key industry that has had its fair share of faux pas (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426100645/image_1426100645.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747482-palo-alto-networks-dont-ignore-warning-signs", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 18:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747476", "title": "ACVF: Why I'm Downgrading This Right-Leaning Conservative Values ETF", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Trump sign\" data-id=\"536863862\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1017px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">SteveChristensen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>The following article is a follow-up to my <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4718410-acvf-high-quality-etf-designed-for-conservative-values-investors\">September 1, 2024, review</a> of the <b>American Conservative Values ETF</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ACVF\" title=\"American Conservative Values ETF\">ACVF</a></span>), a four-year-old actively managed fund with $115 million in assets under management. Previously, I cautioned that ACVF's</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/536863862/image_536863862.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747476-acvf-why-downgrading-this-right-leaning-conservative-values-etf", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 17:47:13", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747486", "title": "New Record High For U.S. October Oil Production", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oil pump, oil industry equipment\" data-id=\"1327982065\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1138px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">bjdlzx</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>A guest post by Ovi</em></p> <p>All of the Crude plus Condensate (C + C) production data, oil, for the US state charts comes from the EIA\u02bcs Petroleum Supply monthly <a href=\"https://www.eia.gov/dnav/pet/pet_crd_crpdn_adc_mbblpd_m.htm\" rel=\"noopener\">PSM</a> which provides updated information up to October 2024.</p> <p></p> <p>U.S. October</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747486-new-record-high-us-october-oil-production", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 17:40:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747473", "title": "QTUM: Investing In Quantum The Right Way", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1453664340/image_1453664340.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A futuristic glowing quantum computer unit, 3d render\" data-id=\"1453664340\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1453664340/image_1453664340.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1453664340/image_1453664340.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1453664340/image_1453664340.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1453664340/image_1453664340.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1453664340/image_1453664340.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1453664340/image_1453664340.jpg?io=getty-c-w480